        "about_quality_text_pursuit": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Premium raw materials raised in the rugged Spanish landscape are carefully washed in Japan and refined into safe, high-quality down. To fully unlock the performance of this down, we employ design methods that combine know-how cultivated through years of experience with data from scientific research in our laboratory, and carefully manufacture products in our factory.</p><p>From material creation to product finishing, and even after-care once our products reach our customers, NANGA is constantly dedicated to the finest craftsmanship.</p>"
          }
        },
        "about_quality_sub_washing": {
          "type": "subheading",
          "settings": {
            "title": "Commitment to Domestic Washing"
          }
        },
        "about_quality_text_washing": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>To bring out the full performance of down, it must be clean and free of impurities. Therefore, we entrust the washing of our down to Kawada Feather, a feather processing manufacturer with proprietary specialized equipment and superior technology. Taking advantage of the ultra-soft underground water nurtured by the rich environment surrounded by mountains and the climate of the Ise Plain in Mie Prefecture, which is ideal for drying feathers, high-quality down is produced.</p>"
          }
        },
