            "title": "Manufacturing by Skilled Artisans"
          }
        },
        "about_quality_text_artisans": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Attention to detail in areas customers cannot see is NANGA's standard. From down filling and sewing to maintenance, because we have our own factory, we can carefully perform each process one by one, creating safe and secure products. By utilizing the skills of experienced craftsmen, product precision is enhanced, leading to the provision of items that satisfy our customers.</p>"
          }
        },
