        "about_quality_text_aftercare": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>The after-care of NANGA products, which has continued since our founding, is the identity of our factory brand. Having our own factory where we plan and manufacture ourselves creates an environment where detailed repair support is possible. This is the reason why customers can confidently choose NANGA products and continue to cherish them for many years.</p>"
